{"tid":1553153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係要加油…俾個石垣伯伯搞喊","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T18:27:58.000Z","uid":40441,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7072441ad075d7725b64a1566a7980e4ab76f92b","tid":1553153,"uid":40441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"話說去咗石垣旅行， 諗住離開香港休息幾日。<br />\n今日去咗一間賣衫嘅鋪頭，都唔出聲啦， 諗住放空行下， 個賣衫阿伯問我係唔係香港人， <br />\n都已經有d 尷尬， 講左聲yes..，就行開左。<br />\n<br />\n點知俾錢果時， 個伯伯又再問係唔係香港人，<br />\n同攞左佢地份報紙， 同我講： Hongkonger fight !Victory!Victory!<br />\n屌，大叔我即場喊左， 係堅好似 攬住隻 熊啤啤咁樣， 攬住個阿伯爆喊&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uM8dwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uM8dwt.jpg&h=e06c726d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb907e962131d2ac35048f42626bf21a5e3ecf0b","tid":1553153,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812f4570e0854ae9c29d1c74fbf2ef6ba84bff4c","tid":1553153,"uid":279810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8790548fcd846bae7d7ccce802a29ddc6ab7400a","tid":1553153,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"205a7aea9073b7f0c53794b670d84208382a2544","tid":1553153,"uid":96930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"你個post有tear gas"},{"pid":"125d19e6b7acb6c77aaddd2374a110f46952f6a3","tid":1553153,"uid":50457,"like":